<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Order Cancelled</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div style="background-color: #f8f8f8; padding: 20px;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Order Cancelled</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 20px;">We're sorry, but your order has been cancelled by the seller.</p>
      <ul style="list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <li><strong>Order Number:</strong> {{orderNumber}}</li>
        <li><strong>Reason for Cancellation:</strong> {{reason}}</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 20px;">We will initiate a refund for your order within 14 business days. Please allow time for the refund to appear in your account.</p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 20px;">If you have any questions or concerns, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
